WEBVTT

1
00:01:32.306 --> 00:01:38.514
(All racers please make your way
to the starting grid.)

2
00:01:39.014 --> 00:01:41.515
(In the pole position is
number 17. Jacky Stewart.)

3
00:01:42.515 --> 00:01:44.251
(In second place on the grid is number 18.)

4
00:01:44.252 --> 00:01:46.413
Hey. What are you doing to my car?
(In second place on the grid is number 18.)

5
00:01:46.615 --> 00:01:47.222
(In third place is Lupin the Third.)

6
00:01:47.223 --> 00:01:49.316
Uh. I'm checking the oil...
(In third place is Lupin the Third.)

7
00:01:50.393 --> 00:01:51.792
Oil. huh?

8
00:01:52.161 --> 00:01:53.492
Well. are you in charge this car?

9
00:01:54.097 --> 00:01:55.292
No. well...

10
00:01:55.699 --> 00:01:56.791
Then I don't need your help.

11
00:01:57.234 --> 00:01:58.929
This car has already been checked.

12
00:01:59.403 --> 00:02:00.370
Yes sir!

13
00:02:03.041 --> 00:02:04.736
Jigen. Lupin here.

14
00:02:05.176 --> 00:02:06.837
A suspicious man showed up here.

15
00:02:07.812 --> 00:02:09.178
By the way. how are things over there?

16
00:02:10.149 --> 00:02:11.810
Here. it is very peaceful.

17
00:02:12.385 --> 00:02:14.478
The birds are singing like Pi-chi-ku.

18
00:02:14.887 --> 00:02:16.753
I don't care about you.
How is my lover...

19
00:02:17.124 --> 00:02:18.648
...Fujiko Mine?

20
00:02:19.059 --> 00:02:19.957
Has she contacted you?

21
00:02:20.427 --> 00:02:21.792
Your lover?

22
00:02:22.162 --> 00:02:24.688
She snuck into the Hotel Miracle.

23
00:02:26.167 --> 00:02:27.600
After that we lost
contact with her.

24
00:02:28.069 --> 00:02:29.536
But I'm sure she'll be fine.

25
00:02:32.941 --> 00:02:35.705
In today's general meeting
we are to discuss...

26
00:02:36.245 --> 00:02:41.149
...the fate of Scorpion's rival. Lupin
the Third. We will conduct his funeral.

27
00:02:41.718 --> 00:02:44.516
True. Lupin is not dead yet...

28
00:02:44.921 --> 00:02:46.253
...but he will die soon enough.

29
00:02:46.857 --> 00:02:50.116
And we shall all bear
witness to his death.

30
00:02:52.396 --> 00:02:56.663
Now then. before we start...

31
00:02:59.705 --> 00:03:00.866
Damn!

32
00:03:04.577 --> 00:03:06.772
This is Jigen. What's happening?

33
00:03:07.547 --> 00:03:09.641
Ah. Jigen. Please contact
Lupin as soon as possible.

34
00:03:10.050 --> 00:03:11.779
Scorpion is going to...

35
00:03:17.158 --> 00:03:21.527
Lupin is Burning?!

36
00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:39.741
I let you run free even though...

37
00:03:40.184 --> 00:03:42.277
...I knew you were up to
something like this.

38
00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.087
You intend to warn Lupin...

39
00:03:45.491 --> 00:03:49.120
...and in doing so ruin
my plan for his funeral.

40
00:03:49.561 --> 00:03:51.529
Isn't that right?

41
00:03:52.565 --> 00:03:54.055
Scorpion. using such an
obvious trick...

42
00:03:54.534 --> 00:03:56.627
It's a bit much. don't you think?

43
00:03:57.237 --> 00:03:59.604
Yes. I do think you will serve nicely...

44
00:03:59.907 --> 00:04:02.273
...as a flower for me
to place on his grave.

45
00:04:03.144 --> 00:04:05.806
Do you want me to be a baton
girl at his funeral?

46
00:04:06.547 --> 00:04:08.175
I am sorry. but I doubt I'll
get a change for that.

47
00:04:08.683 --> 00:04:10.150
Lupin will never die.

48
00:04:10.552 --> 00:04:13.885
In the past maybe.
But this time I can assure you...

49
00:04:14.290 --> 00:04:17.123
I can assure you Lupin will die.

50
00:04:24.701 --> 00:04:28.262
Hyda speedway.
It took 5 years...

51
00:04:28.639 --> 00:04:31.040
...and 5 billion to construct.

52
00:04:31.442 --> 00:04:33.774
It is the largest speedway in the East.

53
00:04:34.212 --> 00:04:38.911
Today. the inauguration of the Formula 1
Grand Prix will take place there...

54
00:04:39.351 --> 00:04:43.515
...and we have used the Japan Racing Association
to invite a certain individual.

55
00:04:44.524 --> 00:04:47.357
The man driving the Ferrari 321.

56
00:04:47.727 --> 00:04:48.716
The man called...

57
00:04:49.162 --> 00:04:50.686
...Lupin the third.

58
00:04:51.132 --> 00:04:53.464
He is indeed a very careful man.

59
00:04:53.835 --> 00:04:55.132
But send him an invitation to a race...

60
00:04:55.770 --> 00:04:57.237
...and he'll always come running.

61
00:04:57.638 --> 00:05:00.164
People are peculiar creatures.
eh. Ms. Mine?

62
00:05:00.475 --> 00:05:01.840
But is this all really worth it?

63
00:05:02.244 --> 00:05:03.836
You've spent 5 billion...

64
00:05:04.279 --> 00:05:06.544
...just to kill Lupin.

65
00:05:07.951 --> 00:05:10.545
What I am going to destroy
is not only Lupin. the man...

66
00:05:11.054 --> 00:05:14.889
...but Lupin. the symbol of the entire
crime empire that depends on him.

67
00:05:15.492 --> 00:05:18.086
If our rivals loose his support...

68
00:05:18.462 --> 00:05:20.954
...their businesses will go under.

69
00:05:22.667 --> 00:05:24.532
The race is about to start.

70
00:05:25.370 --> 00:05:27.930
The track passes through
mountains and valleys...

71
00:05:28.341 --> 00:05:30.502
...and there might even be
a pitfall or two along the way.

72
00:05:30.910 --> 00:05:31.934
Am I right?

73
00:05:32.411 --> 00:05:34.641
We've placed a hundred video
cameras around the track.

74
00:05:34.981 --> 00:05:37.314
They will allow us to
see the entire race.

75
00:05:37.751 --> 00:05:41.050
And Ms. Mine...
As you watch him die...

76
00:05:41.455 --> 00:05:44.016
...you. too. will die.

77
00:06:17.930 --> 00:06:20.161
Jigen. I feel great...

78
00:06:20.633 --> 00:06:21.827
...and my machine feels great. too.

79
00:06:22.268 --> 00:06:24.099
Lupin. I've got the feeling
something's not right.

80
00:06:24.470 --> 00:06:27.201
We lost contact with
her 30 minutes ago.

81
00:06:29.109 --> 00:06:30.804
I see. She must have fallen
for their tricks.

82
00:06:31.512 --> 00:06:32.410
Well. it's OK.

83
00:06:33.747 --> 00:06:35.875
Hey. how is it OK?

84
00:06:36.284 --> 00:06:39.952
CIA's statistics research has shown spies
always reveal themselves sooner or later.

85
00:06:40.522 --> 00:06:41.785
Anyway...

86
00:06:42.191 --> 00:06:44.955
...Fujiko has been caught by them.
and I've fallen into their trap.

87
00:06:45.528 --> 00:06:47.723
I'm going to take the initiative
while their guard is down.

88
00:06:48.097 --> 00:06:49.565
That's the trick to this race.

89
00:06:49.933 --> 00:06:51.298
"Trap"? Did you say "trap"?

90
00:06:52.135 --> 00:06:53.466
I see... This race.

91
00:06:53.837 --> 00:06:54.531
That's right.

92
00:06:54.905 --> 00:06:56.099
All racer and cars...

93
00:06:56.441 --> 00:06:57.373
...appear to be top notch.

94
00:06:58.009 --> 00:07:00.341
John Surtees in a Surtees TS7.

95
00:07:00.712 --> 00:07:02.907
Jackie Stewart in a Ford Tyrrell.

96
00:07:03.214 --> 00:07:04.842
Denny Hulme in a McLaren.

97
00:07:05.718 --> 00:07:07.948
Beltoise in a Matra-Simca.

98
00:07:08.787 --> 00:07:10.254
But in reality...

99
00:07:10.656 --> 00:07:11.988
...they're nothing but imposters.

100
00:07:12.525 --> 00:07:13.924
These car aren't what they seem. either.

101
00:07:14.361 --> 00:07:15.328
I can recognize them by
their engine noise.

102
00:07:15.695 --> 00:07:17.219
These cars were made by the
Scorpion group.

103
00:07:18.766 --> 00:07:21.860
I don't know what kind of trap they
have prepared for me. though.

104
00:07:23.204 --> 00:07:25.729
To find out. I acted like I didn't
know anything and came.

105
00:07:26.441 --> 00:07:27.931
Lupin. stop talking.

106
00:07:28.443 --> 00:07:29.637
A car is closing in on
you from the behind.

107
00:07:30.112 --> 00:07:31.238
It's the Lotus 72.

108
00:07:49.234 --> 00:07:50.599
Lupin. is it Scorpion?

109
00:07:51.069 --> 00:07:51.865
No. it's my nemesis...

110
00:07:52.270 --> 00:07:55.000
...Zenigata from the
Metropolitan Police.

111
00:07:58.911 --> 00:08:00.242
Zenigata...

112
00:08:22.838 --> 00:08:27.569
Lupin. Just how many years
have I followed you like this?

113
00:08:28.545 --> 00:08:31.446
Fate.

114
00:08:31.981 --> 00:08:34.143
If you were not the grandson
of Arsene Lupin...

115
00:08:35.319 --> 00:08:38.152
If I were not a descendant
of Zenigata...

116
00:08:42.260 --> 00:08:44.694
But... I will arrest you.

117
00:08:46.731 --> 00:08:48.529
You pretentious rascal.

118
00:08:49.068 --> 00:08:50.535
Today I will...

119
00:08:51.204 --> 00:08:52.933
...I will finally arrest you.

120
00:08:53.473 --> 00:08:56.034
You must be scheming something big
to appear here today.

121
00:08:56.543 --> 00:08:58.067
I won't take my eyes off your car...

122
00:08:58.512 --> 00:08:59.979
...no matter what happens.

123
00:09:05.487 --> 00:09:06.511
This is the commissioner
to all mechanics.

124
00:09:06.921 --> 00:09:12.126
Get ready to commence Operation:
Lupin the Third Strike Out.

125
00:09:12.795 --> 00:09:13.693
Roger!

126
00:09:14.196 --> 00:09:17.223
Hah. The show is starting.

127
00:09:17.567 --> 00:09:20.593
Well then. let's get started
on this end. too.

128
00:09:46.267 --> 00:09:48.201
We need to make it look like
an accident. Ms. Mine.

129
00:09:48.669 --> 00:09:51.001
Still. nothing less from Lupin.

130
00:09:51.405 --> 00:09:52.963
He survived the
first attempt...

131
00:09:53.375 --> 00:09:55.343
...even while doing
120 kilometers per hour.

132
00:09:56.011 --> 00:09:59.412
His driving skills equal those of
a top level professional.

133
00:10:14.131 --> 00:10:15.120
Damn!

134
00:10:23.342 --> 00:10:25.572
Jigen. It's getting more interesting.

135
00:10:26.178 --> 00:10:27.440
Let's get started.

136
00:10:28.080 --> 00:10:28.978
All right. then...

137
00:12:02.688 --> 00:12:03.848
From the bureau of waterworks?

138
00:12:04.323 --> 00:12:05.449
Checking on a problem?

139
00:12:07.026 --> 00:12:09.051
Yes. I got a phone call
from your company.

140
00:12:09.462 --> 00:12:12.488
Apparently there's a problem
with your employee toilets.

141
00:12:13.199 --> 00:12:15.168
That's strange. Nobody
notified me of this.

142
00:12:15.569 --> 00:12:17.093
Well. if it's a mistake.
guess I'm all done here.

143
00:12:17.571 --> 00:12:19.266
Wait. wait...

144
00:12:19.807 --> 00:12:20.797
Please check anyway.

145
00:12:21.209 --> 00:12:22.107
All right.

146
00:12:26.414 --> 00:12:28.006
Here it is. Please
have a quick look.

147
00:12:28.651 --> 00:12:29.811
Yes sir.

148
00:12:30.586 --> 00:12:33.680
Let's see. the problem was supposedly
in the ladies toilet...

149
00:12:46.137 --> 00:12:48.435
Oh. this isn't good at all.
It's all clogged up.

150
00:12:48.906 --> 00:12:50.636
You're not supposed to
put stuff like this in here.

151
00:13:23.746 --> 00:13:24.405
You're Lupin!

152
00:13:24.947 --> 00:13:25.936
Good night!

153
00:14:06.328 --> 00:14:08.956
Ah! Stop it!

154
00:14:09.665 --> 00:14:10.529
It tickles!

155
00:14:11.166 --> 00:14:13.965
Let me go!

156
00:14:15.271 --> 00:14:17.466
Ah!

157
00:14:18.107 --> 00:14:20.303
Stop it!

158
00:14:30.222 --> 00:14:30.847
Stop it!

159
00:14:31.323 --> 00:14:33.724
How are you feeling?
Lupin is going to die soon.

160
00:14:34.126 --> 00:14:35.889
Wonder what will become of you?

161
00:14:40.868 --> 00:14:42.699
Please open the door!

162
00:14:43.270 --> 00:14:44.294
What's going on?!

163
00:14:44.838 --> 00:14:45.998
Check it!

164
00:14:54.649 --> 00:14:56.117
Wa... Water?!

165
00:14:57.119 --> 00:15:00.247
What's with this water?!
Shut the door quick! Hurry!

166
00:15:01.257 --> 00:15:04.159
It's Lupin. Lupin did it!

167
00:15:04.594 --> 00:15:05.720
What are you talking about?!

168
00:15:07.330 --> 00:15:08.524
See for yourself.

169
00:15:08.865 --> 00:15:10.731
Unless Lupin pulled a miracle...

170
00:15:11.102 --> 00:15:12.660
I already did.

171
00:15:13.604 --> 00:15:14.593
Eh?

172
00:15:18.277 --> 00:15:20.108
Lupin... Lupin...

173
00:15:20.479 --> 00:15:21.309
Lupin!

174
00:15:21.880 --> 00:15:24.781
That's right. In a hotel called "Miracle".
one would expect miracles to happen. no?

175
00:15:25.218 --> 00:15:27.618
Well. let's get on with
Scorpion's funeral.

176
00:15:30.290 --> 00:15:32.350
Shoot him! Shoot him!

177
00:15:51.314 --> 00:15:52.747
Hi there. Fujiko.
How are you feeling?

178
00:15:53.816 --> 00:15:55.910
Oh. I'm feeling all right. Mr. Lupin.

179
00:15:57.020 --> 00:15:58.419
However. I wish...

180
00:15:58.822 --> 00:16:00.449
...you would have
come a bit sooner.

181
00:16:01.258 --> 00:16:05.491
Not at all. I should have
come a bit later.

182
00:16:45.908 --> 00:16:48.434
Zenigata! Your driving
technique is alright...

183
00:16:48.779 --> 00:16:50.144
...but my car is far superior...

184
00:16:50.781 --> 00:16:51.941
...so don't feel bad about this.

185
00:17:24.100 --> 00:17:25.083
Hey. baby.

186
00:17:25.200 --> 00:17:27.844
How did you like Scorpion's?

187
00:17:28.123 --> 00:17:29.351
Umm... It was all right.

188
00:17:30.393 --> 00:17:32.953
What about you? How did
you like being a racer?

189
00:17:36.800 --> 00:17:39.099
Now then. let's finish this.

190
00:18:17.747 --> 00:18:20.375
And now. the victory celebration!

191
00:18:20.783 --> 00:18:22.308
And so...

192
00:18:37.169 --> 00:18:38.966
Damn... I thought that he was going to
do something during the race...

193
00:18:39.371 --> 00:18:41.066
...but the only thing he
stole was away.

194
00:18:41.607 --> 00:18:42.437
Eh?

195
00:18:44.911 --> 00:18:47.675
13... 12... 11...

196
00:18:48.214 --> 00:18:51.673
10... 9... 8... 7...

197
00:18:52.419 --> 00:18:55.183
6... 5... 4...

198
00:18:55.523 --> 00:18:56.512
Hey! Officer!

199
00:18:57.792 --> 00:18:59.283
Present!

200
00:19:13.577 --> 00:19:17.604
After him! After him!

201
00:19:20.017 --> 00:19:21.645
I knew it!

202
00:19:24.055 --> 00:19:25.682
Hey you! Get out of my way!

203
00:19:26.157 --> 00:19:28.319
No can do. If you don't want to die.
you should stay here.

204
00:19:28.661 --> 00:19:29.650
What?!

205
00:19:32.298 --> 00:19:36.861
It's time...
3... 2... 1... zero!

206
00:19:54.423 --> 00:19:57.290
Hey there. Zenigata.
Fancy seeing you here.

207
00:19:57.794 --> 00:19:59.261
Lupin. What the hell?

208
00:20:17.549 --> 00:20:19.210
It's burning! It's burning!

209
00:20:19.484 --> 00:20:21.316
Lupin is burning!

210
00:20:24.790 --> 00:20:27.885
Fire!

211
00:20:37.472 --> 00:20:39.406
Hey you! What did you do?

212
00:20:39.841 --> 00:20:42.003
Now. now. I have an alibi.

213
00:20:42.311 --> 00:20:44.142
You are my witness.

214
00:20:44.580 --> 00:20:45.774
You're with the Metropolitan Police.
remember?

215
00:20:48.651 --> 00:20:51.917
You were right behind my
car during the whole race.

216
00:20:52.489 --> 00:20:54.047
Don't underestimate me. Lupin!

217
00:20:55.225 --> 00:20:58.593
You think that I'm just a
third-class police officer.

218
00:20:58.896 --> 00:21:00.022
But you're wrong!

219
00:21:00.631 --> 00:21:03.099
I know everything you have been doing.
I have a witness.

220
00:21:03.367 --> 00:21:04.528
The jig is up.

221
00:21:05.037 --> 00:21:08.973
This is how it is.

222
00:21:09.341 --> 00:21:12.834
Ah! Jigen! No. I mean...
Who is this guy?

223
00:21:17.583 --> 00:21:18.881
Eh?

224
00:21:19.720 --> 00:21:21.745
Fujiko! You didn't!

225
00:21:22.289 --> 00:21:24.223
That's right.

226
00:21:24.658 --> 00:21:25.556
Fujiko was in on it
from the start.

227
00:21:25.993 --> 00:21:27.359
Lupin. you are under arrest!

228
00:21:29.397 --> 00:21:31.991
Well then. Mr. Zenigata.
We had a deal.

229
00:21:32.500 --> 00:21:33.991
Now give me what you promised.

230
00:21:34.837 --> 00:21:35.826
I'm a man of honor.

231
00:21:36.872 --> 00:21:38.931
Here it is!

232
00:21:39.775 --> 00:21:41.676
An arrest warrant!?
Is it yours?

233
00:21:42.412 --> 00:21:44.346
Yes. I'm a free woman now.

234
00:21:45.515 --> 00:21:47.176
Lupin. I'm sorry.

235
00:21:56.195 --> 00:21:59.824
In other words. freedom is
an important thing to have.

236
00:22:00.399 --> 00:22:04.769
And Lupin. you'll have no
freedom from now on.

237
00:22:07.540 --> 00:22:10.908
Resistance is futile.
Now get going!

238
00:22:12.346 --> 00:22:14.246
Stop resisting already!

239
00:22:14.682 --> 00:22:16.479
You can't escape from me.

240
00:22:40.412 --> 00:22:42.437
Punishment falls upon
the traitor. then?

241
00:22:42.914 --> 00:22:46.577
No way! Betrayal is just another
one of women's accessories.

242
00:22:47.119 --> 00:22:48.279
If I didn't understand
such a thing...

243
00:22:48.687 --> 00:22:49.847
I couldn't love women.

244
00:22:50.256 --> 00:22:51.245
Don't you think?

245
00:22:51.791 --> 00:22:54.351
Stop it! Stop...

246
00:23:07.809 --> 00:23:09.710
Hey. what's up? In next week's episode.
a strange man appears.

247
00:23:10.112 --> 00:23:13.639
His name is Pycal.

248
00:23:14.016 --> 00:23:17.919
bullets bounce off of him and he
throws fire with his finger.

249
00:23:18.321 --> 00:23:20.289
I couldn't do anything
against him.

250
00:23:20.723 --> 00:23:24.023
this man they call a magician.

251
00:23:24.728 --> 00:23:26.218
Please. join the action
in the next episode

252
00:23:31.937 --> 00:23:41.006
Twine itself around my feet

253
00:23:41.681 --> 00:23:48.986
Kick the red waves

254
00:23:51.158 --> 00:23:55.220
Machine scream

255
00:23:55.864 --> 00:24:04.466
It's like a crazy morning light

256
00:24:05.207 --> 00:24:09.577
Walter P-38

257
00:24:10.080 --> 00:24:14.676
In my hand

258
00:24:15.218 --> 00:24:18.620
When I hold it

259
00:24:19.257 --> 00:24:24.389
